OL,3,CTop Labour councillor quits party over
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,FA senior Labour councillor in Dudley
OL,7,Fhas quit the party in protest at the
OL,8,Fgovernment's welfare cuts, accusing
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer of "attacking the
OL,10,Fmost vulnerable in society" and
OL,11,Fsilencing internal criticism.
OL,13,FCllr Pete Lowe, who had been a member
OL,14,Fof the Labour Party for 41 years and
OL,15,Fserved as Leader of Dudley Labour
OL,16,FGroup, announced his resignation in a
OL,17,Fscathing statement on Wednesday. He
OL,18,Fsaid:
