OL,3,CTop Labour councillor quits party over
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,FLowe will now sit as an independent
OL,7,Fcouncillor, joining former Labour
OL,8,Fmembers Steve Edwards and Karen
OL,9,FWestwood, who also left the party
OL,10,Fafter voicing opposition to Starmer's
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,F"My party has left me behind"
OL,15,FIn his resignation letter, Lowe
OL,16,Fdetailed his lifelong commitment to
OL,17,FLabour and the working-class
OL,18,Fcommunities of the Black Country, but
OL,19,Fsaid he could no longer remain in a
OL,20,Fparty that prioritised "the few over
OL,21,Fthe many."
