OL,3,CTop Labour councillor quits party over
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,F"For decades, I could march, protest,
OL,7,Fand campaign proudly with my Labour
OL,8,Fplacards held high. More recently, I
OL,9,Fhave had to show my solidarity
OL,10,Fundercover, fearful that if
OL,11,Fdiscovered, I would be sanctioned from
OL,12,Fwithin."
OL,14,FMr Lowe told me "it's a heartbreaking
OL,15,Fdecision".
