OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,FHe also lamented the erosion of
OL,7,FLabour's core values, saying: "I have
OL,8,Ffinally concluded, and it's
OL,9,Fheartbreaking to say so, that my party
OL,10,Fhas left me behind.
OL,12,F"It has found new friends and
OL,13,Fpriorities in the City and the
OL,14,Fmarkets, while the very people who
OL,15,Flook to the party for a real
OL,16,Falternative, good honest working-class
OL,17,Fpeople in the Black Country and beyond
OL,18,Fhave been abandoned."
