OL,3,CTop Labour councillor quits party over
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,FHis departure adds to growing tensions
OL,7,Fwithin the party over welfare policy,
OL,8,Fwith critics warning that Labour's
OL,9,Fstance is increasingly
OL,10,Findistinguishable from Conservative
OL,11,Fpolicies on public spending.
OL,13,FA West Midlands Labour spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "It is disappointing Councillor
OL,15,FLowe has taken this decision.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
