OL,3,CTop Labour councillor quits party over
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts
OL,6,F"Labour inherited a broken welfare
OL,7,Fsystem from the Conservatives, which
OL,8,Frisked a generation of young people
OL,9,Fbeing written off and millions of
OL,10,Fpeople who want to work not getting
OL,11,Fthe support they need.
OL,13,F"Labour will deliver a social security
OL,14,Fsystem that is fit for the future. One
OL,15,Fthat is fairer, sustainable and that
OL,16,Fprovides vital support to those who
OL,17,Fneed it most."
OL,19,FHowever, for Lowe and others who have
OL,20,Fleft, the shift is a betrayal of
OL,21,FLabour's traditional values.
